Package: opa
Type: Package
Title: An implementation of Ordinal Pattern Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Timothy", "Beechey", email = "tim.beechey@protonmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8858-946X"))
Description: An implementation of ordinal pattern analysis for quantifying
    hypothesis to data fit for repeated measures data, as described by 
    Thorngate (1987) <https://doi.org/10.1016/S0166-4115(08)60083-7> and
    Grice et al., (2015) <https://doi.org/10.1177/2158244015604192>. 
